          <section class="panel"><p class="eyebrow">Recent activity</p><h2>Demo activity feed</h2><div class="activity"><p><b>Today</b><span>Illustrative opportunity refresh prepared three fictional roles for review.</span></p><p><b>Today</b><span>Architecture evidence is ready for the Aurora Relay draft.</span></p><p><b>Yesterday</b><span>Harborlight Works was saved for a later decision.</span></p></div></section>
