          <div class="two-columns"><section class="panel"><p class="eyebrow">Add a fictional lead</p><h2>Turn a note into a reviewable opportunity</h2><label class="field-label">Lead note or example URL<textarea v-model="leadDraft" rows="5" placeholder="For example: fictional referral to a platform leadership role" /></label><div class="actions"><button class="primary" @click="resolveLead">Simulate resolve & score</button><button class="secondary" @click="leadDraft = ''">Clear</button></div><p v-if="leadMessage" class="success">{{ leadMessage }}</p></section><section class="panel"><p class="eyebrow">What happens next</p><h2>Evidence-aware triage</h2><ol class="simple-steps"><li>Capture the opportunity and its source.</li><li>Compare it to the fictional target profile.</li><li>Make the score, evidence, and open questions visible.</li><li>Send it to Top Jobs for a human decision.</li></ol></section></div>
